snippet.title: Peaky Blinders: The King's Ransom - Official Gameplay Reveal Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description:
Based on the hit TV series Netflix and BBC show, Peaky Blinders: The King's Ransom will transport into the world of the Peaky Blinders crime gang that takes place after World War I. This new game will feature appearances by Rowena Fox, Arthur Shelby, Polly Gray, Thomas Shelby, and more. Peaky Blinders: The King's Ransom will be released on Meta Quest and PICO 4 on March 9, 2023.

#IGN #VR
